==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Peucedanin
<hw>Peu*ced"a*nin</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>A tasteless white crystalline substance, extracted from the roots
of the sulphurwort (<gen>Peucedanum</gen>), masterwort
(<gen>Imperatoria</gen>), and other related plants; -- called also
<altname>imperatorin</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Peucil</ent>⟦br⟧
